Scenario Editor
===============

OFFICIAL Scenario Editor core source
Spring engine based in-game tools useful to developers

Installing:
git clone --recursive https://github.com/gajop/Toolbox.git 
(--recursive call will pick up submodules)

Editing modinfo.lua is necessary to run a concrete mod

Example files can be found in the examples/ dir

Running examples (Linux):
#cd into Toolbox.sdd dir
spring $PWD/examples/$example_name.txt

#Running a game (needs BAR in modinfo.lua):
spring $PWD/examples/trolol.txt

#Running a game in dev mode (needs BAR in modinfo.lua):
spring $PWD/examples/trolol-dev.txt
